&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calling all Registered General Nurses &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for something different for the next step in your career?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Something that builds on all the knowledge and skills you already have?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An opportunity to be part of an excellent team that is &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Committed to delivering excellent patient care, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excited to innovate to improve the way different services work together and &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Passionate about having an amazing place to work for all the team &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Then this opportunity has your name on it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust have embarked on a journey drawing together the expertise in medicine services to create a truly joined up service for the patient poulation we serve. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for keen enthusiastic registered nurses, experienced and newly qualified to join our dynamic caring team, working in Medicine and specialist medical areas. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a rewarding, and busy service delivering high quality care across all our medical wards. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Viola Nube - viola.ncube@btuh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
